"2  garlic cloves","1 1/2 teaspoons kosher salt","1 teaspoon grated fresh ginger","1/4 cup grated onion (use a Microplane)","1/4 teaspoon cayenne","2 teaspoons ground coriander","2 teaspoons ground cumin","1/2 teaspoon ground allspice","1/2 teaspoon pepper","1/4 cup finely chopped flat-leaf parsley","1 1/2 pounds ground beef (at least 20 percent fat for a juicier burger)","  Olive oil for brushing pita","3  pita breads","  About 3/4 cup store-bought tzatziki","  Cucumber and tomato slices, butter lettuce, and fresh mint leaves"